{"label": "droite", "transcript": [{"text": "Madam President,", "start": 0.583, "duration": 0.967}, {"text": "the crisis we are experiencing", "start": 1.55, "duration": 0.966}, {"text": "forces us all to come back to reality,", "start": 2.516, "duration": 2.634}, {"text": "particularly in terms of energy,", "start": 5.15, "duration": 1.916}, {"text": "to get out of our dependencies,", "start": 7.066, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "to protect the environment.", "start": 8.366, "duration": 1.134}, {"text": "We no longer have the right to illusions.", "start": 9.5, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "You want", "start": 11.6, "duration": 0.816}, {"text": "to massively develop wind power,", "start": 12.416, "duration": 1.017}, {"text": "and you gave the example of Denmark", "start": 13.433, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "as a model.", "start": 14.633, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "But with nearly 10,000 wind turbines,", "start": 15.533, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "Denmark remains dependent", "start": 17.033, "duration": 1.417}, {"text": "on its coal-fired power stations,", "start": 18.45, "duration": 1.633}, {"text": "and must import electricity:", "start": 20.083, "duration": 1.517}, {"text": " the energy which neighboring Sweden produces", "start": 21.6, "duration": 2.483}, {"text": "and exports is 50% less carbon -intensive", "start": 24.083, "duration": 2.217}, {"text": "thanks to... nuclear power.", "start": 26.45, "duration": 1.766}, {"text": "How can we get out of the impasse", "start": 28.216, "duration": 1.45}, {"text": "if we don't open our eyes?", "start": 29.666, "duration": 1.267}, {"text": "If we send gas to Germany", "start": 30.933, "duration": 1.7}, {"text": "to help it get through the winter,", "start": 32.633, "duration": 1.383}, {"text": "while letting it", "start": 34.016, "duration": 0.684}, {"text": "shut down its operating nuclear power plants?", "start": 34.7, "duration": 2.333}, {"text": "If to stop paying for Russian gas,", "start": 37.033, "duration": 1.717}, {"text": "we pay for Azeri gas,", "start": 38.75, "duration": 1.616}, {"text": "thus becoming dependent on", "start": 40.366, "duration": 1.267}, {"text": "another criminal dictatorship?", "start": 41.633, "duration": 1.833}, {"text": "And I dare to hope, Madam President,", "start": 43.466, "duration": 1.734}, {"text": "that we will together sanction", "start": 45.2, "duration": 1.566}, {"text": "the aggression launched yesterday", "start": 46.766, "duration": 1.317}, {"text": "by Aliyev against Armenia.", "start": 48.083, "duration": 1.733}, {"text": "It's not just about energy.", "start": 49.816, "duration": 1.834}, {"text": "Coming back to reality", "start": 51.65, "duration": 0.966}, {"text": "means refusing these new rules", "start": 52.616, "duration": 1.967}, {"text": "which will lower", "start": 54.583, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "agricultural production in Europe,", "start": 55.333, "duration": 1.483}, {"text": "while food prices are", "start": 56.816, "duration": 1.467}, {"text": "rising everywhere in our countries.", "start": 58.283, "duration": 1.85}, {"text": "It's starting to produce again,", "start": 60.133, "duration": 1.117}, {"text": "rather than betting", "start": 61.25, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "on the multiplication", "start": 62.15, "duration": 1.283}, {"text": "of dated trade agreements.", "start": 63.433, "duration": 1.25}, {"text": "It is to break with the spiral of a common debt", "start": 64.683, "duration": 2.417}, {"text": "which will make us vulnerable tomorrow.", "start": 67.1, "duration": 1.766}, {"text": "It means defending Frontex", "start": 68.866, "duration": 1.767}, {"text": "and controlling our borders,", "start": 70.633, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "rather than undermining its mandate.", "start": 71.716, "duration": 2.35}, {"text": "It's not", "start": 74.066, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "just recruiting talent abroad,", "start": 75.116, "duration": 1.55}, {"text": "but it's first and foremost", "start": 76.666, "duration": 0.667}, {"text": "better training our young people.", "start": 77.333, "duration": 1.317}, {"text": "You want,", "start": 78.65, "duration": 0.333}, {"text": "Madam President,", "start": 78.983, "duration": 0.717}, {"text": "to include solidarity", "start": 79.7, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "between generations in our treaties", "start": 80.9, "duration": 2.3}, {"text": "and we share this spirit,", "start": 83.216, "duration": 1.667}, {"text": "but it probably starts there.", "start": 84.883, "duration": 2.667}, {"text": "Thanks a lot.", "start": 87.55, "duration": 1.7}]}